text: Martyna Mikołajczak (born 12 May 1991) is a Polish rower. She competed in the women's lightweight double sculls event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bydgoszcz Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
